title: Man shot in foot on Capitol Hill
text:
A man was shot in the foot, and a driver said bullets hit his car and became lodged in a seatâ€”during an early morning shooting on Capitol Hill.
Police heard gunshots and flooded the area along Harvard Avenue, where they located an injured man.
He was taken to Harborview for treatment of injuries, at around 2:45 a.m.
No suspects were located.
If you have any information, call police at: (206) 233-5000.
